{"title":"友善R4S软路由刷系统","slug":"友善R4S软路由刷系统","date":"2025-06-25T06:56:50.000Z","updated":"2025-06-28T00:41:16.270Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/友善R4S软路由刷系统.json","excerpt":" [Figure] NanoPi R4S 友善R4S 友善之臂RK3399开发板, 刷系统, 恢复软路由功能","covers":["https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2025/06/25/685b9ecfb11ba.png","https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2025/06/28/685f39a79f09e.png","https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2025/06/28/685f39ca95030.png"],"content":"<img class=\"lozad\" data-src=\"https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2025/06/25/685b9ecfb11ba.png\">\n\n<p>NanoPi R4S 友善R4S 友善之臂RK3399开发板, 刷系统, 恢复软路由功能</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<div> \n<button onclick=\"synthesizeSpeech()\">朗读全文</button>\n</div>\n<audio controls id=\"audioPlayer\">Your browser does not support the audio element.</audio>      \n<script>\n  function synthesizeSpeech() { \n    var inputText = document.getElementsByClassName('post-block')[0].innerText;\n    var voice = \"ZH\";\n    var url = 'https://tts.carlzeng.com:3/speech?text=' + encodeURIComponent(inputText.substring(0,3000)) + '&voice=' + voice;\n    var audioPlayer = document.getElementById('audioPlayer');          \n    audioPlayer.src = url;\n    audioPlayer.load();\n    audioPlayer.play();\n  }\n</script>\n\n\n<h1 id=\"有什么用\"><a href=\"#有什么用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"有什么用\"></a>有什么用</h1><p>了解大致的R4S刷软路由系统的过程</p>\n<p>解决R4S红灯, 路由功能失效等故障</p>\n<p>实际应用: 使用openwrt中的passwall然后连接到机场, 使内部局域网整个网络可无缝访问国际互联网</p>\n<h1 id=\"相关内容\"><a href=\"#相关内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"相关内容\"></a>相关内容</h1><iframe style=\"box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px -10px;\" src=\"https://query.carlzeng.com:3/appsearch?q=软路由\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"auto\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"工具\"><a href=\"#工具\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"工具\"></a>工具</h1><ol>\n<li>R4S固件:</li>\n</ol>\n<p>已测试(稳定 好用): <a href=\"https://file3.carlzeng.com:3/d/Aria2%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9/2025-01-01-openwrt-rockchip-armv8-friendlyarm_nanopi-r4s-ext4-sysupgrade.img.gz\">2025-01-01-openwrt-rockchip-armv8-friendlyarm_nanopi-r4s-ext4-sysupgrade.img.gz</a></p>\n<p>​\t如果想要最新版的, 更全面的插件, 可以尝试</p>\n<p>​\t<a href=\"https://file3.carlzeng.com:3/d/Aria2%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9/bleachwrt-plus-20250625-rockchip-armv8-friendlyarm_nanopi-r4s-squashfs-sysupgrade.img.gz\">bleachwrt-plus-20250625-rockchip-armv8-friendlyarm_nanopi-r4s-squashfs-sysupgrade.img.gz</a></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>刷机工具Rufus</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://rufus.ie/downloads/\">https://rufus.ie/downloads/</a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"实现方法-步骤\"><a href=\"#实现方法-步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现方法&#x2F;步骤\"></a>实现方法&#x2F;步骤</h1><p>先刷入原厂固件</p>\n<p>在通过原厂固件刷入第三方的固件</p>\n<ol>\n<li>准备32G的sd卡 和读卡器; 插入Windows电脑</li>\n<li>用Rufus 工具, 给这张SD卡刷写系统, 系统文件可选用</li>\n<li>2025-01-01-openwrt-rockchip-armv8-friendlyarm_nanopi-r4s-ext4-sysupgrade.img.gz</li>\n</ol>\n<p>刷入成功后;  拔卡插入R4S机器</p>\n<p>开机, 绿灯;  连接Lan口的网线到电脑</p>\n<p>根据当前PC自动获取到的IP地址, 尝试连接到R4S的管理页面, 浏览器打开: 192.168.1.1; 192.168.2.1</p>\n<p>可正常使用OPENWRT</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2025/06/28/685f39a79f09e.png\" alt=\"image-20250628083900617\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://img.carlzeng.com:3/i/2025/06/28/685f39ca95030.png\" alt=\"image-20250628083937248\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"网络拓扑图\"><a href=\"#网络拓扑图\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网络拓扑图:\"></a>网络拓扑图:</h2><p>猫 - R4S - 路由器&#x2F;交换机&#x2F;电脑</p>\n<h1 id=\"灵感来源\"><a href=\"#灵感来源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"灵感来源\"></a>灵感来源</h1><p><a href=\"http://www.aiothome.net/read.php?tid-974.html.html\">友善之臂NanoPi&#x2F;6818&#x2F;4418&#x2F;4412&#x2F;210&#x2F;6410&#x2F;2451&#x2F;2440&#x2F;2416资料汇总贴</a> </p>\n<p>。NanoPi-R4S<br><a href=\"https://wiki.friendlyelec.com/wiki/index.php/NanoPi_R4S\">https://wiki.friendlyelec.com/wiki/index.php/NanoPi_R4S</a></p>\n","more":"<div> \n<button onclick=\"synthesizeSpeech()\">朗读全文</button>\n</div>\n<audio controls id=\"audioPlayer\">Your browser does not support the audio element.</audio>      \n<script>\n  function synthesizeSpee